{"tid":1788143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"女警的海鮮 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88e04d7947db525abb7fcf6d54ee6b5743efe0a5","tid":1788143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191218/20826870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826870%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6mt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=60031593\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826870%2F&h=ee77dcd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191218/20826870/</a><br />\n<br />\n女警的海鮮 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191218/large/1576574002_0b4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576574002_0b4b.jpg&h=0a383f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商場和你shop，黑衣年輕人又再被拉被鎖，黑警制服多人後扯其面罩，露出一張中學四眼妹女生的臉。黑警包圍理大13日，拘捕千人裏面，中學生三百多人。之後的人鏈活動，黑警喺正校門拉人，中學生在石屎地上以黑字寫上：你支持的警察殺人了，便衣女警即刻撲出，制服女學生後把她的頭當凳坐。女警的「海鮮」有此特殊用途，我好擔心，被拉的女同學，會不會被加控非禮？以後見到海鮮炒飯，作嘔是必然的了。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕齋shop唔買，年輕人做得到嗎？荃灣那家日本殿堂，開張幾日都有人龍。老海鮮那杯茶的維園工展會，記者訪問一店家，滿以為老闆大吐滯銷苦水，點知老細嘴角含春，猛話生意好過去年，「內地顧客多嗎？」老闆笑得更甜：「得幾個咋，今年幫襯的全部香港人！」直接向鳩噏預警的陳茂波打臉，打柒巴！而TG過門不入的半島酒店，聖誕自助餐迅速訂滿，豪客不存在九億補水未落袋的1.1萬個popo。popo冇資格去半島，亦唔幫襯美心救亡，識伍淑清個海鮮！九億明益海底撈！撐警奀星衰曝光，廣告代言冇得再撈，只能繼續腦殘，自虐扮浮屍，向警大喊：海底見！ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"fc18db0397604796552e8f9e171589a15c20d285","tid":1788143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}